To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private HeikinAshi _heikinashi;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_heikinashi = HeikinAshi(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_heikinashi.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "open", _heikinashi.Open.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "high", _heikinashi.High.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "low", _heikinashi.Low.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "close", _heikinashi.Close.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "volume", _heikinashi.Volume.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "heikinashi", _heikinashi.Current.Value);
}
